{"tid":510270,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"煎鍋貼","createTime":"2017-12-26T09:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T10:49:41.000Z","uid":123364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"08fc26686be4e4ae9e1f8031d95c9ce165bb025f","tid":510270,"uid":123364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T09:43:58.000Z","msg":"有冇人中意自己係屋企剪鍋貼食？ <br />\n以前食開呢隻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/26/171654_77583bf4a190a45642e5cb2eda15687c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F26%2F171654_77583bf4a190a45642e5cb2eda15687c.jpeg&h=053e76e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以前厚皮多汁好好味<br />\n頂幾年前轉撚左口味 變左標榜所謂皮薄函靚<br />\n即刻變左垃圾<br />\n<br />\n之後試左好多隻都係皮薄款<br />\n得罪講句<br />\n所有皮薄既都係垃圾<br />\n根本就唔撚係鍋貼<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知仲有邊隻厚皮鍋貼賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"40a4afb8e8268d896dfb39c02604845d7106f14d","tid":510270,"uid":46835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:37:52.000Z","msg":"呢隻我都試過中招<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c06ffcf9fd63b79c7760bb5075227cde8b44f3","tid":510270,"uid":72608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:46:55.000Z","msg":"轉左皮之後好垃圾<br />\n好似膠片皮咁"},{"pid":"b383a489b053152a1b38133d6e2eaa18cc57c8a0","tid":510270,"uid":60453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"轉左買依個牌子既小籠包黎煎 好撚正"},{"pid":"a2753a98c7352a7edefa4c9be1739e923a1e2480","tid":510270,"uid":48276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"買鍋貼大王果D啦<br />\n同佢講買生既返去自己煎"}]}